title: The Wholefood Kitchen
description: An all-vegan (and organic/spray-free) pop-up restaurant held every Friday night at The Organic Apple Cafe. (Please note that the cafe does serve meat at all other times.) The chef rents the cafe for the night and produces a menu of three vegan dishes for $12 ($6 for children) - price as of Feb 2016. Open until the food runs out. Bring your own containers for take-out.
